00:49:50.330 --> 00:49:50.960
19. 20.

00:49:50.960 --> 00:49:51.640
¡Para!

00:49:51.650 --> 00:49:52.300
21.

00:49:52.300 --> 00:49:52.900
25.

00:49:52.930 --> 00:49:53.410
Siéntate ahora.

00:49:53.410 --> 00:49:54.130
26.

00:49:54.130 --> 00:49:54.830
27.

00:49:54.830 --> 00:49:55.630
¡Para!

