Levántate.

00:49:58.100 --> 00:49:59.450
Hey, te queda un deseo.

00:49:59.450 --> 00:50:00.390
¡50!

00:50:00.630 --> 00:50:01.230
51.

00:50:01.310 --> 00:50:02.600
52, 53.

00:50:02.610 --> 00:50:03.540
54, 55.

00:50:03.540 --> 00:50:04.900
¡Para!

00:50:06.890 --> 00:50:13.760
Di, "Oppa... lo siiiennto."

